>## 7th Legion Footman
>*Medium humanoid (Human), neutral*
>___
>- **Armor Class** 20 (plate armor, shield)
>- **Hit Points** 97 (15d8 + 30)
>- **Speed** 30 ft.
>___
>|STR|DEX|CON|INT|WIS|CHA|
>|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|
>|16 (+3)|12 (+1)|14 (+2)|10 (+0)|10 (+0)|12 (+1)|
>___
>- **Skills** Athletics +6, Intimidation +4
>- **Senses** passive Perception 10
>- **Languages** Common
>- **Challenge** 5 (1,800 XP)
>- **Proficiency Bonus** +3
>___
>***Determination.*** When the footman makes an attack roll, an ability check, or a saving throw, it can do so with advantage. The footman can't do so again until you finish a short or long rest.  
>
>***Martial Advantage.*** Once per turn, the footman can deal an extra 7 (2d6) damage to a creature it hits with a weapon attack if that creature is within 5 feet of an ally of the footman that isn't incapacitated.  
>
>### Actions
>***Multiattack.*** The footman makes three weapon attacks.  
>
>***Longsword.*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* +6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. *Hit:* 7 (1d8 + 3) slashing damage, or 8 (1d10 + 3) slashing damage if used with both hands.  
>
>### Bonus Actions
>***Shieldwall.*** The footman takes cover behind its shield. Gaining +2 to its armor class and dexterity saving throws, but has its bonus to attack rolls is reduced by 2.

